    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const inputData = $input.first().json;\nconst name = inputData.customerName || 'Guest';\n\nconst reply = `✂️ *Glamour Unisex Salon* mein aapka swagat hai, ${name}! 🌟\n\nNiche reply karo:\n\n1️⃣ *book*\n2️⃣ *menu*\n3️⃣ *staff*\n4️⃣ *offer*\n5️⃣ *status*`;\n\nreturn {\n  from: inputData.from,\n  to: inputData.to,\n  customerName: inputData.customerName,\n  intent: inputData.intent,\n  replyText: reply\n};"
      },
